Class Diagram
Classes:
Book

Attributes:
title: String
author: String
isbn: String
numPages: int
Methods:
getters and setters for all attributes
toString(): String (for printing book details)
Library

Attributes:
name: String
location: String
books: ArrayList<Book>
Methods:
addBook(book: Book): void
removeBook(isbn: String): void
findBookByTitle(title: String): Book
Relationships:
Book ↔ Library: Aggregation (Library has an ArrayList of Books)
Library → Book: Dependency (Library uses Book instances)
